With Eskom already having been deemed as the single biggest threat to the economy, has the latest bouts of load shedding undone all the positive sentiments and renewed investment promises made at this year’s Mining Indaba? To speak on the issue and what the future for mining holds, Richard Damant, associate: Advisory, Nedbank CIB, joins Nompu Siziba in studio. <a href="https://iono.fm/e/654459">Content hosted by iono.fm</a>